# Rockae monorepo folder (`C:\GIT\Rockae`)

**Canonical local clones** live under **`C:\GIT\Rockae\`**, not `C:\GIT\CommunityBuilder.*`.

**This workspace** is **`CommunityBuilder.Models`** — shared Django schema (`app_models.*`). **Not** an HTTP API. Migrations are **applied** from **`CommunityBuilder.DataMigration`**.

## Schema workflow (pair with DataMigration)

| Repo | Local path | GitHub |
|------|------------|--------|
| **Models (this repo)** | `C:\GIT\Rockae\CommunityBuilder.Models` | [CommunityBuilder.Models](https://github.com/MyRockae/CommunityBuilder.Models) |
| **DataMigration** | `C:\GIT\Rockae\CommunityBuilder.DataMigration` | [CommunityBuilder.DataMigrations](https://github.com/MyRockae/CommunityBuilder.DataMigrations) |

## Services that depend on this package

| Service | Local path | Production |
|---------|------------|------------|
| **Main API** | `C:\GIT\Rockae\CommunityBuilder.API` | [https://api.rockae.com](https://api.rockae.com) |
| **Payment API** | `C:\GIT\Rockae\CommunityBuilder.Payment` | [https://payment.rockae.com](https://payment.rockae.com) |
| **Notification API** | `C:\GIT\Rockae\CommunityBuilder.NotificationService` | [https://notification-api.rockae.com/](https://notification-api.rockae.com/) |
| **MES** | `C:\GIT\Rockae\CommunityBuilder.MES` | [https://mes.rockae.com](https://mes.rockae.com) |

Each pins a commit in `requirements.txt` — bump after model changes are merged and migrations applied.

## User-facing apps (indirect)

Portal and mobile use the **shared Postgres schema** via Main API + Payment; they do not import this package directly.
